Experience a romantic getaway in our Honeymoon Retreat. This intimate & beautifully decorated suite is designed for couples celebrating their love. The suite features a luxurious king-size bed with romantic canopy, private balcony with stunning views, and a spacious bathroom with a deep soaking tub for two.

Enjoy a complimentary bottle of champagne upon arrival and savor a romantic dinner in the privacy of your suite.
